                    <div class="column-block">
                        <h2 class="fs-title">Car Seats</h2>
                        <p>New York State law requires all motor vehicle passengers ages 8 and older to wear seat belts, regardless of seating position. Children under the age of 4 must ride in a car seat and
                            children under the age of 2 must ride in a rear-facing car seat.</p>
                            
                        <p>You can bring your own car seat(s) and your chauffer will be happy to assist you in securing the car seat to the vehicle or you can request a car seat(s) to be pre-installed. The charge for car seats are $40 for first seat and $25 for additional car seats.</p>
                            
                        <label class="radiocontainer">I will need assistance with my car seats
